&lt;h1 id="配置">配置&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="npm-镜像设置">&lt;code>npm&lt;/code> 镜像设置&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://mirrors.tencent.com/help/npm.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>腾讯解君愁&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="hugo-设置自定义域名">Hugo 设置自定义域名&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参见 &lt;a class="link" href="https://gohugo.io/hosting-and-deployment/hosting-on-github/#use-a-custom-domain" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Use a Custom Domain&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="hugo-中嵌入-html-的方法">Hugo 中嵌入 HTML 的方法&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>于 &lt;code>config.yml&lt;/code> 中加入以下配置：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yml" data-lang="yml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">markup&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">goldmark&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">renderer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">unsafe&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>参考 &lt;code>Hugo&lt;/code> 文档 &lt;a class="link" href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration-markup#goldmark" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Goldmark&lt;/a> 一栏。&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>unsafe&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>By default, Goldmark does not render raw HTMLs and potentially dangerous links. If you have lots of inline HTML and/or JavaScript, you may need to turn this on.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="hugo-papermod-主题安装更新方法">Hugo PaperMod 主题安装、更新方法&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参考其教程即可 &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod/wiki/Installation" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Hugo PaperMod&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="hugo-papermod-本地查看静态页面异常">Hugo PaperMod 本地查看静态页面异常&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>打开 &lt;code>public/index.html&lt;/code>，查看控制台报错。&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Access to CSS stylesheet at &amp;lsquo;file:///PATH/TO/FILE.css&amp;rsquo; from origin &amp;rsquo;null&amp;rsquo; has been blocked by CORS policy: Cross origin requests are only supported for protocol schemes: http, data, chrome-extension, edge, https, chrome-untrusted.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>跨源请求不支持 &lt;code>file&lt;/code> 协议，所以将：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">link&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">crossorigin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;anonymous&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">href&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;/assets/css/FILE.css&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">rel&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;preload stylesheet&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">as&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;style&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">/&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>修改为：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">link&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">crossorigin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;anonymous&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">href&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;http://DOMAIN.YOUR.SITE/assets/css/FILE.css&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">rel&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;preload stylesheet&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="na">as&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;style&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">/&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>即可。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="git-配置代理">Git 配置代理&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参见&lt;a class="link" href="https://ericclose.github.io/git-proxy-config.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>一文让你了解如何为 Git 设置代理&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/quickstart/set-up-git" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Set Up Git&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="我的-git-配置">我的 Git 配置&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git config --global user.name &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;xqm32&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git config --global user.email &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;458173774@qq.com&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git config --global http.https://github.com.proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="git-mediawiki">Git-MediaWiki&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参见&lt;a class="link" href="http://members.wolfram.com/meng/pages/computing/installing_and_configuring/installing_and_configuring_git-mediawiki/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Installing and configuring Git-Mediawiki&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="winget">WinGet&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>可以使用 WinGet 进行软件包的安装，如：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">winget install --id Git.Git -e --source winget
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>参见&lt;a class="link" href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Git Downloads&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="nvm-配置问题">NVM 配置问题&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参见&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/wiki/Common-Issues#permissions-exit-1-exit-5-access-denied-exit-145" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Permissions (Exit 1, Exit 5, Access Denied, Exit 145)&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="wsl">WSL&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="wsl-自启动">WSL 自启动&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>仅在 Windows 11 下有效。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参见 &lt;a class="link" href="https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/windows/wsl/wsl-config#boot-settings" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>WSL 自启动&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="更换-ustc-镜像">更换 USTC 镜像&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo sed -i &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;s/archive.ubuntu.com/mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/g&amp;#39;&lt;/span> /etc/apt/sources.list
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="wsl-2-配置代理">WSL 2 配置代理&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>若使用 &lt;code>bash&lt;/code>，则在 &lt;code>.bashrc&lt;/code> 中添加：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">windowsHostIP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sb">`&lt;/span>cat /etc/resolv.conf&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>grep nameserver&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{print $2}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sb">`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">proxy&lt;span class="o">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">ALL_PROXY&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;http://&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$windowsHostIP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">:10809&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">all_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;http://&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$windowsHostIP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">:10809&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;http://&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$windowsHostIP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">:10809&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;http://&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$windowsHostIP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">:10809&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">unproxy&lt;span class="o">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">unset&lt;/span> ALL_PROXY
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">unset&lt;/span> all_prox
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">unset&lt;/span> http_proxy
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">unset&lt;/span> https_proxyy
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>虽然看起来没有必要，但是只有设置了 &lt;code>http_proxy&lt;/code> 和 &lt;code>https_proxy&lt;/code> 才能对 &lt;code>wget&lt;/code> 生效，笔者感觉十分奇怪。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考 &lt;a class="link" href="https://syz913.github.io/2021/03/20/wsl2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>WSL2 网络代理设置&lt;/a> 和 &lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.skk.moe/post/enable-proxy-on-ubuntu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Ubuntu「一键」设置代理&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="wsl-与加速器产生冲突">WSL 与加速器产生冲突&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>注意&lt;/strong>：此方法可能有副作用。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>WSL 与加速器的冲突可以参考此文章解决 &lt;a class="link" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/151392411" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>关于使用 WSL2 出现“参考的对象类型不支持尝试的操作”的解决方法。&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="wsl-中-cc-调试报错的解决方案">WSL 中 C/C++ 调试报错的解决方案&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkdir -p /build/报错路径（如 glibc-XXXXXX）
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/glibc/需要的 glibc 如（glibc-X.XX.tar.gz）
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo tar xf glibc-X.XX.tar.gz --directory&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/build/glibc-XXXXXX/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h1 id="软件">软件&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="markdown-编辑器">Markdown 编辑器&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;del>由于 &lt;a class="link" href="https://typora.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Typora&lt;/a> 收费且收费较贵，不得不寻找其替代品，目前感觉 &lt;a class="link" href="https://marktext.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>MarkText&lt;/a> 比较不错。&lt;/del>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://typora.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Typora&lt;/a> 真香 🤣。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="windows-工具">Windows 工具&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>由于我的键盘的 &lt;code>ctrl&lt;/code> 键坏了，需要将 &lt;code>CapsLock&lt;/code> 键映射到 &lt;code>ctrl&lt;/code> 上，于是发现了这个好用的小工具：&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/microsoft/PowerToys" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Microsoft PowerToys&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>它还有一些其他好用的功能，比如双击 &lt;code>ctrl&lt;/code> 键可以快速的找到你的鼠标在哪儿。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="流程图uml-画图工具">流程图、UML 画图工具&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://draw.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Draw.io&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="windows-拼音输入法错误修复">Windows 拼音输入法错误修复&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>参考 &lt;a class="link" href="https://answers.microsoft.com/zh-hans/windows/forum/all/%e5%be%ae%e8%bd%af%e6%8b%bc%e9%9f%b3%e8%be%93/a462b2f3-9db2-4313-9369-f1ff8ec07975" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>微软拼音输入法&lt;/a>，关闭输入法的 &lt;code>智能模糊拼音&lt;/code> 和 &lt;code>模糊拼音&lt;/code> 可以暂时修复。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="ios15-拼音输入法错误修复">iOS15 拼音输入法错误修复&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;del>关闭 &lt;code>滑行输入&lt;/code> &lt;strong>似乎&lt;/strong>可以暂时修复。&lt;/del>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考 &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.v2ex.com/t/820760" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>这个帖子&lt;/a>，&lt;strong>似乎&lt;/strong>可以暂时修复。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="aria2c-仅下载种子不下载文件">Aria2c 仅下载种子，不下载文件&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>运行时加入 &lt;code>--follow-torrent=false&lt;/code>，参见 &lt;a class="link" href="https://aria2.github.io/manual/en/html/aria2c.html#cmdoption-follow-torrent" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>&amp;ndash;follow-torrent&lt;/a> 参数。&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="开发">开发&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="github-贡献">GitHub 贡献&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>添加功能或者修复错误时，应创建新的分支而非从 main/master 直接推送。&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Contributing to GitHub&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Contributing to Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead is easy — simply fork the repository here on GitHub, make your changes, and then send us a pull request.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>There are a couple of guidelines we suggest sticking to:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Add this repository as an upstream remote.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Keep your master branch clean. This means you can easily pull changes made to this repository into yours.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Create a new branch for each new feature or set of related bug fixes.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Never merge from your local branches into your master branch. Only update that by pulling from upstream/master.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="wsl-安装-rust">WSL 安装 Rust&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Rust 官方给出了安装工具 &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.rust-lang.org/zh-CN/tools/install" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>安装 Rust&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="游戏">游戏&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="无名杀">无名杀&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/libccy/noname" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>无名杀&lt;/a>的一种少错误的安装方法：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>下载https://github.com/libccy/noname/releases/download/SSS/Windows_Yuri_Fix.zip；&lt;/li>
&lt;li>下载&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/libccy/noname/archive/refs/heads/master.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>最新源代码&lt;/a>；&lt;/li>
&lt;li>解压游戏客户端至当前文件夹，应当会出现 &lt;code>./Windows_Yuri_Fix/noname&lt;/code> 或 &lt;code>./noname&lt;/code> 文件夹，后面我们以 &lt;code>./noname&lt;/code> 文件夹为&lt;strong>游戏目录&lt;/strong>；&lt;/li>
&lt;li>将最新源代码（即资源文件）解压，应当会出现 &lt;code>./noname-master&lt;/code> 文件夹，将文件夹中的全部内容移动至&lt;strong>游戏目录&lt;/strong>下 &lt;code>./resources/app&lt;/code> 文件夹，即可启动游戏。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>下载&lt;a class="link" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/L-yCzP0JTOajMbRC3kAq_Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>「在线更新」拓展&lt;/a>并在游戏中导入，进行更新即可。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
